Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:13.24,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Apoptoxin 4869.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:18.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A poisonous drug used for assassinations, developed by the Organization I used to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:23.16,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}High school detective Shin'ichi Kud√¥ took the drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.83,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and by an accidental use of its cellular selfdestruction program,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:30.25,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}his body reversed to the state of a first-year primary school child
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:31.76,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}instead of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:39.18,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And I too, in order to escape from the Organization, chose the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:50.27,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now we're primary school students, and the Organization still doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.53,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If we were to be found out, then not just us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.16,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but everyone associated with us would also be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:04.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Our first crisis... came that day without any warning whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A desperate crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:09.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A magnificent revival turns the case's solution around!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:12.05,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Another meeting with the men in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:14.21,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What fate awaits the cornered Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:16.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:18.26,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:20.18,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you watch yesterday's match?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You mean Hide's overhead kick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time for games is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, wake up from your dream and celebrate our reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In pure red blood, like the color of your favorite rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh...? Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the game I borrowed from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell the doctor that it was even better than we hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boss character was a bit lame, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was still better than the one in the previous game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, snow's falling! Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:20.47,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's celebrate our reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:26.90,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In pure red blood, like the color of your favorite rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:30.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eh...? Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come look out of the window at the snow with us, Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of this place already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish I could just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, one of these days, I probably will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are you transferring to another school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that someone's bullying you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please don't say you're leaving us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just joking! Don't take me so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got a bit of a cold, so I'm in just a bad mood. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I shouldn't be in this place."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"To avoid getting these kids involved,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I have to disappear from this place as soon as possible."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of nonsense you're thinking right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The idea that someone would shrink from a drug is just absurd. Nobody would believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long as you keep acting as a child, you can stay under cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:31.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kudo{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}, you still don't know a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:36.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You can't handle something like them by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:41.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once you let your guard down, it's all over. The Organization won't let us get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:46.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right. Maybe, just like in my dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even now, somewhere in this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}they're watching us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Is there something wrong with that black Porsche?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Porsche 356A.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 50-years old classic car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The driver doesn't seem to be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin's favorite car is one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gin's, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you bring them with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Yeah. A metal clothes hanger and a wrench.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you need them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To open an old car, all you have to do is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm planting a transmitter and receiver inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we're not even sure this is their car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gin! Vodka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The snow's unusually tattered around the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some civilians probably came and looked at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your car is quite rare nowadays, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The German Rainfrog."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure became famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:45.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:48.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I never thought I'd find them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:51.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm glad I did, Gin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are things on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? He still hasn't shown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The target's sure to show his face at the Haido City Hotel, at 6 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:17.14,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He has no idea it'll be his own farewell party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:20.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Target? Farewell party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, our superior ordered us to kill him before he rats us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Feel free to use that drug if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.62,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't mess it up, Pisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pisco?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A reddish brown hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bro, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.98,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's probably a transmitter and receiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, they found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:13.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I never thought you'd be the one to approach me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:17.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I welcome you, Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez... I thought you had no interest in things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't help it. I'm the one who made that drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't want you to call me a murderer anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they happen to suspect that the one who planted those devices would come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if they find out you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you already erase all the evidence in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll think it's either a prank, or that someone who's against the Organization did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, are you sure this is their meeting place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin said it's a farewell party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pisco and his target should both be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:29.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn. It's a mourning party, so lots of people are wearing black.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Everybody's starting to look suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sherry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:42.00,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sherry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:47.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, little girl? Did you get separated from your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're looking for them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hana{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}. {hana - short for hanako = flower. But I really don't think there's a point to keeping this in a TL note, it's completely irrelevant to this case}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you? This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one who chose to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On my way home, Gin saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He chased me into an alleyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you were the first one he shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with each reload of his gun, everybody else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just because they were involved with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe if the Organisation'd killed me back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we wouldn't have as much hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know? Nobody'll ever discover your identity if you wear those.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even Clark Kent would be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then, having taken off the glasses, does that make you Superman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a famous director's mourning party, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are lots of well-known faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, then? Did you figure out who Pisco's target is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin mentioned on the phone that the target would arrive at 6 PM,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that he might be arrested by the police tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so it can only be that man in the entrance, who's surrounded by reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:38.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,Shigehiko Nomiguchi (56)\NLawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he's the lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who the papers all say is taking bribes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please answer more clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave him a phone call from the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told him someone wants to murder that lawyer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:14:03.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,Naomichi Mugikura (43)\NAnnouncer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:14:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me to present you with a slide-show
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of Director Sakamaki's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone, do any of you know when and where this photo was taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait. That lawyer's gone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up and find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is the work that made Director Sakamaki famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The place where he filmed "The Rainbow Handkerchief."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still haven't found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look more carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now let's look at the next photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? This looks like the studio cafeteria's staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ok, let's move on to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A flash?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how precious this photo is, you wouldn't be able to see it if you used a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were the ones closest to Mr. Nomiguchi when the chandelier fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see anyone suspicious at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:48.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,Yoshiharu Tawara (58)\NUniversity Professor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was almost crushed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:51.83,Signs,,0,0,0,,Chris Vineyard (29)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never saw any suspicious characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, she says she didn't see anyone of the sort, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was an accident, an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:06.39,Signs,,0,0,0,,Naoya Tarumi (35)\NMusic Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chandelier's chains were weak and broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lawyer just happened to be under it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was a message saying there'd be a murder tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:18.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kenz≈ç Masuyama (71)\NPresident of a car factory
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know more about the sender.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The voice was altered by a machine, so we don't even know if it was a man or a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it was probably a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:29.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Naomichi Mugikura (43)\NAnnouncer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nomiguchi was weakened by his medical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The accident just happened to overlap with the prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:40.67,Signs,,0,0,0,,Yasuo Mihei (62)\NOwner of a pro baseball team
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The heavens smited him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't do bad things, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you eat at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An insignificant lad like yourself should keep his mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Someone call the chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Was there a cockroach in it or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:04.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're eating at a time like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the heavens smited you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is... a piece of the chandelier's chain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was it in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:20.54,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mika Nanj≈ç (38)\NAuthoress
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nomiguchi died when he was crushed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by the falling chandelier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To murder someone that way, you'd have to set a trap on the chandelier,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,lure him underneath it when the lights were turned off,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then activate the trap, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, looking at the fallen chandelier or the ceiling it hung from,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, murder is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you understand, could you release us already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dropping a chandelier on a targeted individual without some sort of trap would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Staying here and wasting time is too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You only have one clue: The piece of chain you picked up earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not even you could figure out who the criminal is from just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if I have two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It fell after the chandelier, but before the lights were turned back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like it has the criminal's name written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at its corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It says "Director Sakamaki's Mourning Party," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its owner probably received it at the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just look around at the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, that man holding the glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the overweight woman next to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the elderly man with the mustache in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they all have this handkerchief, but in different colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:18:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Likely, due to Director Sakamaki's number one hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Rainbow Handkerchief," handkerchiefs in 7 different colors were given to the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, if we ask at the front desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we can reduce the number of suspects to those that received a purple handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can go to the toilet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Mr. Nomiguchi really pass away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll explain it later, so please everyone, back away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Please answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The people we gave purple handkerchiefs to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I picked one up, so I want to return it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guests who were given purple handkerchiefs are these seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So it was one of those seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not certain, but it's likely that among those seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is one of them, Pisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, they're coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn. Let's go back to the doc's car for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wai‚Äî
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.77,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Haibara? Is that you, Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:05.06,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm in the doc's car in front of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking to you through the microphone and speaker in the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.57,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to know! What happened in the hallway, in front of the party room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In front of the party room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, back then I got engulfed by a wave of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and got separated from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.17,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then someone came from behind me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.84,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone came from behind you and...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody made me sniff some drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and now I'm being confined in some wine storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:42.43,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey... By "somebody," you mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Likely the Organization member who managed to commit murder in front of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not there, is he? Is he nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:22:01.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Whoever he is, he's not here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the door is locked tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing around is a large cardboard box and cart for carrying goods
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and some employee overalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:13.00,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Overalls?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Likely, after making me sniff the drug, he must have taken me to the toilet or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,changed into these previously prepared overalls, then stuffed me in the box and brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably ready in case the attempt on that lawyer's life failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd have lured the lawyer to the toilet and killed him, then brought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:37.53,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Whatever. Just hurry and find a way out of there, and find our next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.11,0:22:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Apoptoxin 4869 that shrunk our body's {\i1}apopto{\i0} uses {\i1}apoptosis{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, programmed cell destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:22:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.17,0:22:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, this drug doesn't just activate {\i1}apoptosis{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It also includes Telomerase, and increases a cell's reproductive ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Haibara! I'll listen to as much as you want about that once you get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.68,0:23:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up and listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll never... never be able to exchange words with you ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:19.44,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They held me here despite being in my shrunken figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I were to escape from here, they'd find me in no more than two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:39.05,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If that happens, the doctor who protected me, and all others who were involved with me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:42.63,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}would be killed to preserve their secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.89,0:23:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter if I die here or if I escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already been forced into a state where I can no longer come into contact with any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:56.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.94,0:24:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I'm going to tell you all I know about the drug, as long as I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:07.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tadah! Dr. Agasa's Great Adventure II!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.66,0:24:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.87,0:24:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the doctor's game that Tsuburaya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} returned to me at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were probably checking the M.O. in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.38,0:24:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a cell phone attached to the laptop, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.60,0:24:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.26,0:24:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were analyzing my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.72,0:24:33.27,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, you aren't tied down?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.89,0:24:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.23,0:24:40.82,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They won't leave me for long without tying me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.82,0:24:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he won't be able to come back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.03,0:24:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you disappeared, I called the inspector right away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.24,0:24:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and told him to not let the guests with purple handkerchiefs leave the Haido City Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.50,0:24:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with Shin'ichi Kudo's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.71,0:25:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this place is still somewhere in the Haido City Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.96,0:25:03.76,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.76,0:25:09.68,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I can prove the murder before he contacts his companions, and bring him to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.68,0:25:13.22,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}then your secret will remain intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.73,0:25:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At best, the inspector can hold those seven for another hour or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.52,0:25:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going to the hotel's front desk
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.15,0:25:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to ask them if there's any unfrequently used wine storage room in the hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.23,0:25:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I'll go and save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.57,0:25:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.86,0:25:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you what'd happen to those involved with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.62,0:25:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me for what happens to people who chose to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.67,0:25:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then find some way to get out of there by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.42,0:25:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's really easy to say and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.84,0:25:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there's no escape route in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.26,0:25:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing here is an old chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.97,0:25:51.72,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can you climb up that chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.31,0:25:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's too big to climb up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.56,0:26:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I wasn't in this body, it looks like I could barely manage it by stretching my arms and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.48,0:26:04.40,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't there some sort of rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.49,0:26:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not sure. Do they keep ropes in a wine storage room?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.49,0:26:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's a wine storage room, does it mean it has a wide variety of alcoholic drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.58,0:26:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there baigar there?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.66,0:26:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Baigar?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.62,0:26:18.37,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah. It's a strong liquor from China.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.37,0:26:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.92,0:26:21.38,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just look around for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.38,0:26:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see if there's some.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.88,0:26:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what do you want that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.05,0:26:28.17,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How's your cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.17,0:26:30.64,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You said you had a cold in the morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.64,0:26:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your topic seems to jump all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.39,0:26:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever, just tell me how you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.47,0:26:40.10,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After my sleeping on the floor, I think my fever went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.10,0:26:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.31,0:26:42.15,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.15,0:26:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sound quite happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.40,0:26:46.19,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.32,0:26:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found the baigar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.86,0:26:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what am I supposed to do with this liquor?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.91,0:26:55.58,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm going to get you out of that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.08,0:26:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By casting the ultimate magic spell on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.25,0:27:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lupin III vs...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.75,0:27:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.00,0:27:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On March 27th at 9 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.76,0:27:15.68,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This part was brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.64,0:27:23.46,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}This was the scene inside the hotel, right after the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.46,0:27:29.44,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Even now, many people are still being questioned in a nearby room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.44,0:27:32.91,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}However, those individuals' names have yet to be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.91,0:27:35.24,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That is all. This is being broadcast live from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.99,0:27:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From that news report, I figured out the rough location of the seven right after the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.62,0:27:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.42,0:27:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how do you spell "Hercule Poirot?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.92,0:27:51.26,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What the heck are you doing? Did you drink the baigar already?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.26,0:27:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.72,0:27:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're planning, but I feel even worse now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.89,0:28:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, tell me how to spell Poirot's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.19,0:28:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want to know that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.23,0:28:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to transfer the drug's data from the Organization's computer to the doctor's M.O.,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.32,0:28:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I got stuck on the password.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.45,0:28:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...R-O-T.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.20,0:28:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no good. It's not Poirot.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.91,0:28:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you think the password might be "Poirot?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.83,0:28:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The people in the Organization called the drug by a name during its prototype phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.92,0:28:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They gave it the serial number 4869/{\i1}shiyaroku{\i0} after Sherlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.64,0:28:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They called it "the incomplete Great Detective."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.72,0:28:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I've been trying the names of Great Detectives as they popped into my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.77,0:28:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I guess it's not going to be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.19,0:28:48.65,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Shelling Ford."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.11,0:28:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The spelling is "S-H-E-L-L-I-N-G F-O-R-D."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.90,0:28:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does such a detective even exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.57,0:28:57.70,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just try it and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.70,0:29:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-H-E-L-L-I-N-G F-O-R-D.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.79,0:29:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It opened! How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.13,0:29:10.80,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Shelling Ford" was...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.17,0:29:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...a temporary name that Conan Doyle gave to his detective before naming him Sherlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.93,0:29:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's the prototype of the Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.64,0:29:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's kind of clever for the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.93,0:29:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.73,0:29:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't your body feel odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.81,0:29:33.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could it not, after you had me down liquor like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.82,0:29:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, I'll drop the drug's data on this M.O. and hide it in this wine storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.87,0:29:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can come and get it after the Organization takes me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.12,0:29:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.54,0:29:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shi... Shin'ichi! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.05,0:29:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's them. Could Pisco have gotten through to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.09,0:30:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that can't be! The Inspector said he'd call me before releasing those seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.02,0:30:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.02,0:30:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could there be a tracer in the PC Haibara's using?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.98,0:30:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it. They called him and there was no answer, so they used the tracer to get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.65,0:30:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.07,0:30:22.37,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They're coming! For now, go hide in the chimney or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.99,0:30:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.99,0:30:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.61,0:30:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pisco's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.90,0:31:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was supposed to contact us 30 minutes after finishing off the target, but he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.99,0:31:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we came here thanks to the tracer, and the laptop's here, but not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.66,0:31:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just where'd he disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.83,0:31:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's the deal with this wine storage room?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.80,0:31:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pisco probably prepared this room just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.43,0:31:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he'd failed in the party room, he'd probably kill him elsewhere, and bring him here afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.14,0:31:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, we shouldn't stick around too long, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.69,0:31:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.28,0:31:49.29,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, did they leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.29,0:31:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.62,0:31:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And uh... your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.83,0:31:53.67,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.29,0:31:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing the overalls that were left in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.30,0:32:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I have the M.O. with the copy of the drug's data, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.34,0:32:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised. That baigar liquor...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.18,0:32:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it has some enzyme that speeds up cellular metabolism or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.39,0:32:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get too relieved, it's only temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.90,0:32:19.23,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Get out of that chimney before you turn back into a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.23,0:32:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.74,0:32:25.62,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}By the way, have you figured out who Pisco is?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.62,0:32:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.37,0:32:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't enough information.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.74,0:32:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this, Shin'ichi. Tomorrow's news photo is on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.21,0:32:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say a cameraman in the room took it right before the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.13,0:32:43.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait! Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.13,0:32:45.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A burn mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.80,0:32:48.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means this chain...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.68,0:32:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.35,0:32:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.69,0:33:00.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Haido City Hotel, Old Building
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.25,0:33:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I missed you... Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.42,0:33:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you knew I'd be coming out of this chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.31,0:33:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was this hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.02,0:33:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found this reddish-brown hair of yours near the chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.73,0:33:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could have killed you inside that dirty chimney,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.61,0:33:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I thought I could at least let your death flower bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.78,0:33:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my. I guess I should thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.20,0:33:56.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For waiting for me in this cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.04,0:34:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you while those lips still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.50,0:34:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you disappear from the Organization's gas room?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.47,0:34:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? A wine storage room?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.22,0:34:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I think it has a big chimney in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.73,0:34:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do we even have a room like that in this hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.02,0:34:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's in the old building that's going to be rebuilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.69,0:34:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old building?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.86,0:34:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I heard they were using a room somewhere as a temporary storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.99,0:34:30.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Storage... that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.20,0:34:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Haibara was shot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.25,0:34:41.17,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, on a roof somewhere. Hurry and g‚Äî
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.50,0:34:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, doc! Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.17,0:34:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, the battery must've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.38,0:34:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.56,0:35:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bro, this girl's not gonna talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.31,0:35:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.36,0:35:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's send her to meet her sister, whom we sent first.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.80,0:35:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A needle?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.94,0:35:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.73,0:35:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.57,0:35:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get into the chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.86,0:35:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.99,0:35:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.04,0:36:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bro? What's wrong, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.17,0:36:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.72,0:36:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were still a baby, so you probably don't remember anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.39,0:37:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I was very close to your parents, who were scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.06,0:37:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told a lot about the drug during development.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.07,0:37:08.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.44,0:37:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I had no clue that you managed to take it to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.36,0:37:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your parents, who died in that accident, would've been very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.41,0:37:20.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.41,0:37:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is an order, so don't blame me,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.88,0:37:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.50,0:37:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.21,0:37:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masuyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.51,0:37:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or should I call you Pisco?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.43,0:37:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who... Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.52,0:37:49.06,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You might think you skillfully dropped the chandelier on Mr. Nomiguchi's head to make it look accidental,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.44,0:37:51.44,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but things never go that smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.44,0:37:53.57,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You dropped it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.03,0:37:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a silencer-equipped handgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.61,0:38:02.37,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Your target was the fluorescent substance you painted on beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.24,0:38:08.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once the lights go out in the room from the slideshow, that light will shine through.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.17,0:38:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, if you'd fired at it directly, there'd be a spark from your gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.30,0:38:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which would be noticed by the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.51,0:38:18.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But if you cover the silencer with a handkerchief,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.26,0:38:24.47,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the handkerchief will fly off with the bullet and hide the spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.47,0:38:28.06,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The reason you used the handkerchief from Director Sakamaki's mourning party
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.06,0:38:32.36,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}was because it'd be hard to trace even if it was found later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.36,0:38:38.36,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But of the guests who received that purple handkerchief, most went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.36,0:38:40.45,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And so the suspects became just those seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.99,0:38:47.41,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tawara{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10} and Chris{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}, being directly under the chandelier with no way to aim, are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.41,0:38:50.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mihei{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}, who spat out the chain piece that became evidence from his mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.67,0:38:53.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and Mugikura{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}, who'd been watched by the guests on-stage, didn't do it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.75,0:38:59.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tarumi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10} and Nanj≈ç{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}, who were embracing each other right before the incident, are also clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.38,0:39:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the only one that could have committed this crime was you, Masuyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.64,0:39:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.31,0:39:15.69,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the reason Mr. Nomiguchi went under the chandelier
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.69,0:39:19.95,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}was because you put fluorescent material on the floor there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.36,0:39:23.53,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You probably told him you could give him a chance to avoid being arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.53,0:39:28.62,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and to wait for you at the glowing place once the light faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.62,0:39:30.79,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't that right, Pisco{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.37,0:39:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A speaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.00,0:39:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who... Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.79,0:39:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.96,0:39:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan Edogawa, detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.63,0:39:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De... Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.84,0:39:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that {\i1}you{\i0} were the one giving out orders to the police during their investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.14,0:39:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and the two above will be caught by the police sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.27,0:39:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that, could you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.82,0:40:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you have that purple handkerchief during the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.16,0:40:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the Inspector had to release you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.24,0:40:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that handkerchief have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.45,0:40:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are things in this world that you don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.00,0:40:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And look at the situation. You won't be able to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.21,0:40:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.09,0:40:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.68,0:40:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spirytus.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.56,0:40:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strong wine, with 96% alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.56,0:40:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know what happens if you smoke near that much alcohol, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.78,0:40:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fire has erupted in room 404 of the old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.95,0:40:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I repeat, a fire has erupted in room 404 of the old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.16,0:40:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.08,0:40:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.63,0:40:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.71,0:41:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come out, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.59,0:41:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.30,0:41:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.27,0:41:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Gin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.77,0:41:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you messed up, Pisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.27,0:41:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you immediately kill that cameraman or got rid of the film?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.69,0:41:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cameraman? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.61,0:41:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's paper has been replaced by your photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.70,0:41:34.46,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It shows you holding your gun to the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.62,0:41:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do it! If you kill me, you'll never find Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.29,0:41:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a general idea of her whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.80,0:41:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if you kill me, who served {\i1}that{\i0} person for so many years, then your standing will...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.97,0:41:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.80,0:41:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was a direct order from {\i1}that{\i0} person.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.40,0:42:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Gin executed Pisco?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.28,0:42:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was listening to the conversation through the glasses Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} forgot in the chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.03,0:42:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think he ran away through the chimney right after killing Pisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.66,0:42:19.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange. How can he move after I shot him with the tranquilizer gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.04,0:42:24.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I thought a huge guy like him wouldn't be able to get away from the police, once put to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.51,0:42:29.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm also worried about how well they read Haibara's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.39,0:42:34.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It seems like they {\i1}knew{\i0} she was going to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.26,0:42:38.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could they really tell it's her just from one strand of hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.40,0:42:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haibara? When you were in the Organization, were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.19,0:42:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, did they find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.44,0:42:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That my body shrunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.36,0:42:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think they know. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.20,0:42:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what are you planning to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.29,0:43:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.87,0:43:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that they know that I'm in this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.46,0:43:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stay with you guys any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.88,0:43:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the M.O. in those overalls is probably burnt up by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.39,0:43:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for me to stay here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.31,0:43:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll leave first thing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.85,0:43:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you can't do that with your body like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.15,0:43:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, then everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.20,0:43:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not going to search this city for that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.29,0:43:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm a {\i1}sh≈çgun{\i0} who doesn't do useless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.04,0:43:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's probably long gone by now, with that man who came to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.04,0:43:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not a stupid enough woman to stay in a city where we saw her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.05,0:43:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, it looks like you're quite caught up with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.22,0:43:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Vermouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.43,0:44:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We called a lady like you to help that old geezer,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.94,0:44:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and got you into such a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.65,0:44:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, to think I even gave him that handkerchief before he went into questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.99,0:44:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he ended up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.16,0:44:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you wonder about the man with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.63,0:44:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the man who is embraced by that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.80,0:44:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd love to see his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.84,0:44:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. His dead face consumed by fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.68,0:44:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going back to America?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.56,0:44:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to take a break from being an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.56,0:44:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I plan to relax in Japan for a while. There's something I'm involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.37,0:46:26.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So you watched until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.95,0:46:31.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And there you go. Now you're one of the people who knows our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.54,0:46:36.59,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In other words, if the Organization finds us, you'll be killed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.09,0:46:43.93,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why we have to be careful to not get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.51,0:46:47.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that you yourself can continue to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.11,0:47:04.62,Signs,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. No matter what happens,\NI will protect you all.
